title: Meat Puppets - Live at the Southern (2013)_320kbps_mp3
description:
Live Meat Puppets show from Oct. 6, 2013 at the Southern Cafe & Music Hall, Charlottesville, Va. Made with an Olympus WS-311M, cleaned up with Goldwave 5.58. Beautiful extended versions of "Touchdown King", "Up On the Sun", "I'm a Mindless Idiot", Everley Brothers' "Cathy's Clown", "Lake of Fire" ... excellent show, thanks Pups...
